---
---
<section class="concepto" id="concepto" aria-label="Concepto y diferenciador">
  <div class="concepto-container">
    <!-- CONCEPTO -->
    <div class="section-header" data-animate>
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Nuestra Esencia</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Cocina del Alma</h2>
      <div class="title-ornament"><span></span><span class="diamond">◆</span><span></span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="concepto-grid" data-animate>
      <div class="concepto-text">
        <p class="lead-text">
          En <em>Pixán Cocina del Alma</em> transformamos ingredientes selectos en experiencias memorables a través de una propuesta de cocina contemporánea internacional.
        </p>
        <p>
          Nuestra esencia combina sabores, técnicas y tradiciones gastronómicas de distintas partes del mundo, reinterpretadas con creatividad, elegancia y un toque único.
        </p>
        <p>
          Cada platillo es elaborado cuidando cada detalle, desde la selección de ingredientes frescos hasta su presentación, ofreciendo una experiencia que despierta todos los sentidos.
        </p>
        <div class="concepto-tags">
          <span class="tag">Desayunos</span>
          <span class="tag">Entradas</span>
          <span class="tag">Pastas</span>
          <span class="tag">Cortes</span>
          <span class="tag">Mariscos</span>
          <span class="tag">Especialidades</span>
          <span class="tag">Postres</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ESPACIO PARA FOTO 1 -->
      <div class="concepto-image-slot" id="concepto-foto-1" aria-label="Espacio para foto del restaurante">
        <img src="/fotos/restaurante.jpg" alt="Interior Pixán" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .concepto {
    background: #0a0000;
    padding: 7rem 2rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .concepto::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #c0141c, transparent);
  }
  .concepto-container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .section-header.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c0141c;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: #fff;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }
  .title-ornament {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .title-ornament span { display: block; width: 60px; height: 1px; background: rgba(192,20,28,0.4); }
  .title-ornament .diamond { color: #c0141c; font-size: 0.6rem; }
  .concepto-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease 0.15s, transform 0.7s ease 0.15s;
  }
  .concepto-grid.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  .lead-text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #e8ddd0;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }
  .concepto-text p {
    color: rgba(232,221,208,0.75);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .concepto-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .tag {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #c0141c;
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,20,28,0.3);
    padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  .tag:hover { background: rgba(192,20,28,0.1); border-color: #c0141c; }
  .concepto-image-slot {
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    border: 1px solid rgba(192,20,28,0.25);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: rgba(20,5,5,0.6);
  }
  .image-upload-zone {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    border: 2px dashed rgba(192,20,28,0.2);
    margin: 1.5rem;
  }
  .image-upload-zone img {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
  .upload-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; opacity: 0.5; }
  .upload-label {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: rgba(232,221,208,0.6);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .concepto-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .concepto-image-slot { aspect-ratio: 16/9; }
  }
</style>
